Author: soclosetoit
Text: This has been my life. It’s like a switch flips. Ultra-restriction no problem, then give it a few months or years and I can’t do anything to stop binge eating. I don’t understand it, and I definitely can’t control it...

Author: Rosalie_aqua
Text: Omg this is me. I can relate so much, today eating has made me feel sick and I’m not hungry at all but yesterday I was starving and ate like 800 calories of cake :(
